{"word":"H2740 - חָרֹון - chârôwn - khaw-rone' - Sore displeasure","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָרֹון</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>chârôwn"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-rone'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Sore displeasure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"கோபம், உக்கிரம், எரிச்சல், சூடேறுதல் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"anger, heat, burning (of anger); always used of God's anger"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H2734 - חָרָה - chârâh - khaw-raw'/2734\">H2734</a>; a <i>burning</i> of anger: - sore displeasure, fierce (-ness), fury, (fierce) wrath (-ful)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2734 - חָרָה - chârâh - khaw-raw'/2734\">H2734</a>, <a href=\"#/H2739 - חֲרוּמַף - chărûwmaph - khar-oo-maf'/2739\">H2739</a>, <a href=\"#/H2740 - חָרֹון - chârôwn - khaw-rone'/2740\">H2740</a>, <a href=\"#/H2750 - חֳרִי - chŏrîy - khor-ee'/2750\">H2750</a>, <a href=\"#/H8474 - תַּחָרָה - tachârâh - takh-aw-raw'/8474\">H8474</a>"}]}